<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000791>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Aleuromarginatus glandulis Dubey sp. nov., holotype puparium: (a) dorsal and ventral views; (b) cephalothorax, eye spots; (c) abdominal segments, wax glands; (d) thoracic tracheal comb; (e) vasiform orifice; (f) ventral fold, setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000791/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000801>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Aleuromarginatus martini Dubey sp.nov., holotype puparium:(a) dorsal view; (b) antenna; (c) abdominal segments I and II, submedian pores; (d) posterior abdominal area." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000801/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000819>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Aleuromarginatus sulawesiensis Dubey sp. nov., holotype puparium, line drawings: (a) dorsal and ventral views; (b) margin; (c) abdominal segments, depressions, setae; (d) vasiform orifice; (e) legs and antenna. VS- ventral setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000819/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000805>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Aleuromarginatus martini Dubey sp. nov., holotype puparium, line drawings: (a) dorsal view; (b) margin; (c) abdominal segments, sutures; (d) eye spots on prothorax; (e) vasiform orifice, posterior abdominal setae; (f) eighth abdominal setae; (g) eye spot on lateral longitudinal line. Arrow – eye spot." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000805/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000823>
    dc:description "Figure 16. Aleuromarginatus sulawesiensis Dubey sp. nov., holotype puparium: (a) dorsal and ventral views; (b) cephalic margin; (c) thoracic tracheal pore area; (d) abdominal subdorsal area; (e) abdominal segments, depressions, submedian setae; (f) posterior abdominal area; (g) vasiform orifice." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000777>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Aleuromarginatus asymmetricis Dubey sp. nov., holotype (a, c, d) and paratype (b) puparium, line drawings: (a) dorsal and ventral views; (b) abdominal depressions, setae; (c) posterior abdominal area, caudal setae; (d) legs and antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000777/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000779>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Aleuromarginatus asymmetricis Dubey sp. nov., holotype (b, c, h) and paratype puparium (a, d–g) puparium: (a) dorsal view; (b) dorsal and ventral views; (c) margin, thoracic tracheal pore area; (d) cephalothorax; (e) abdominal segments, depressions, submedian setae; (f) posterior abdominal area, vasiform orifice; (g) caudal fold, ventral setae; (h) antenna, prothoracic leg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000785>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Aleuromarginatus frim Dubey sp. nov., holotype puparium: (a) dorsal view; (b) abdominal segments, submedian setae; (c) cephalothorax, thoracic tracheal comb; (d) vasiform orifice." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000785/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000817>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Aleuromarginatus similis Dubey sp. nov., holotype puparium: (a) dorsal view, tubercles, setae; (b) abdominal segments I–IV; (c) margin, submargin; (d) abdominal segments V–VIII; (e) posterior abdominal area; (f) vasiform orifice; (g) ventral setae; (h) antenna, female; (i) prothoracic leg, antenna, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6000817/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

